        "text": "Inventories of retail merchants.\u2014The retail method of pricing inventories does not contemplate valuation of goods at the retail selling price. The retail selling price of goods on hand must be reduced to approximate cost or cost or market, whichever is lower, by the adjustments required in Regulations section 1.471-8."
